title: Gov't Mule - 'Mighty High' [320k MP3]
description:
Mighty High is an album released by Gov't Mule on October 16th, 2007. Mighty High features reggae and dub versions of classic Mule covers and originals with special guest appearances by reggae legends Michael Franti, Toots Hibbert, and Willi Williams. Most tracks on Mighty High were recorded in the studio but a few of the songs are remixed dubstyle from live recordings at the Beacon Theatre, Bonnaroo, and Mountain Jam.
